    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/1db8367b4163852e0920cce2a6cfc618.avif?t=1752805196\" width=630 height=275 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/3b59893b9cebb334a472aec262b72c8d.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/9b7aa1c3977fd38cbca03d1af4ca9c57.avif?t=1752805196\" width=639 height=160 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/ad1e23bd1cffc17894278c392b9d06e1.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/fbec20dac997e0440dd636e0178bc538.poster.avif?t=1752805196\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/fbec20dac997e0440dd636e0178bc538.webm?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/fbec20dac997e0440dd636e0178bc538.mp4?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/dad69d77401ef6980a204dde5cf65df6.poster.avif?t=1752805196\" width=800 height=456 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/dad69d77401ef6980a204dde5cf65df6.webm?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/dad69d77401ef6980a204dde5cf65df6.mp4?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/3e634f5abf4e78a709338184336dc802.poster.avif?t=1752805196\" width=800 height=457 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/3e634f5abf4e78a709338184336dc802.webm?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/6b9d0b252fd4b36bc7f78f401666dc5d.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你在一个陌生的地方醒来，失去了所有记忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个叫 “ <strong>艾琳 </strong>” 的年轻女子正在照看你，她说是来治疗你的失忆症，但一切看起来都不对劲儿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你真的可以信任她吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因为某种原因，你只能说“知道了”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被困在狭小的四方房间里，再加上失去记忆的状态，这一切未免也太奇怪了吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一切为时已晚之前，必须寻找真相并找到逃出去的办法吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/b652be95c8f221c6849150f637191651.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>👁️‍🗨️ 解谜挑战     </strong>探索每个房间，寻找线索，逐步解锁下一关。每当打开新房间，剧情都会推进，同时紧张感也会升级。<strong>    <br>     <br>👁️‍🗨️你的选择决定剧情   </strong>你的每个决定都会影响故事的发展，结局是好是坏，完全取决于你的选择。<strong> <br> </strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>👁️‍🗨️三个结局    </strong>游戏有三个结局，每个结局都与你的行动息息相关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果错过了某些关键点，可能会影响你发现真相的机会。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/1f97bbba4c4d65a1696b1b46bb849aa9.avif?t=1752805196\" width=639 height=160 /></span></p>",
